simplesect.para: You get the pointer to the sparse solutions stored in the constraint handler (not a copy).

The sparse solutions are stored w.r.t. the active variables. This are the variables which got not removed during presolving. For none active variables the value has to be computed depending on their aggregation type. See for more details about that COLLECTALLFEASEBLES.
